##My head. I like it

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
February 17,2020.

The 24th day of the 1st Lunar Month.

Day 26 of the siege of Wuhan.

The 25th day the gate of Heaven is sealed.

In the midday sun, my uncle pushed my hair. I looked in the mirror and shaved my beard. For the first time in my life, I grew up visible to the naked eye. And then I took a shower, and it was nice. Dad brought the razor. I lost mine in Wuhan. If I'd known I was GONNA be locked up this long, I would have brought him back.

I haven't dated Tony since I bought a razor in Shanghai four years ago, and I don't have a building more than 3 cm above my head, and I'm not bothered that my washed-up head is out of shape again. My mother-in-law's comment was, "where's the money? Don't you see you're saving money? Grow a bald gun (like a convict in a Labor Camp! ") Back six years ago, when I was in Guangzhou, I was trying to grow my hair and beard to the length of my life, which required a headband. New Year back is also a burst of grandmother Scold, said no boy to stay so long hair, not like a person! Let uncle "hold me" to cut. I'm fun myself, and I don't want to go against the old people. And it's hard to keep your hair straight -- at least until you wash it every two days. But really, after the "vexation silk" has been cut off, the people are all a lot more pure.

What I want to say is that the older generation's stereotypes can not be corrected, much less criticized, and they are also the victims of brainwashing. The body of the parents, but if therefore bound, controlled, sacrifice, there is no understanding of the individual, self-respect, it is still a violation of the individual power. Like the one above with the shaved head. Shaving my head, I understand. The publicity of shaving my head, it's almost disgusting. Of course, is always moved by the group of "not shaved head" of the people.
